{"tid":1029200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲仔扮豪客闖英皇鐘錶 偷百萬名錶當場斷正","createTime":"2019-02-20T05:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T04:09:11.000Z","uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1e26491903f2f6d3b95d4a6113af63b3960c5123","tid":1029200,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"灣仔發生店舖盜竊案，晚上7時許，現場為軒尼詩道288號地下英皇鐘錶珠寶店，警方接獲33歲姓黃職員報案，指懷疑一名18歲姓陳男子盜去兩隻總值約102萬的勞力士手錶。警員接報到場，於陳男身上搜出兩隻勞士力手錶。警方將案件列企圖店舖盜竊，陳男涉案被捕。案件交由灣仔警區刑事調查隊第2隊跟進。"},{"pid":"76f31dfb2556e056a11fdfd8e842f816a7c9f8f9","tid":1029200,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:41:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a132c7d112f8c7cc266a96bc0dfb8bff159df623","tid":1029200,"uid":3232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:09:13.000Z","msg":"傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7161178a221d3d356eef39a0cb6a556314786861","tid":1029200,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"連登仔不嬲幻想自己動作快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd643510e5d46cbffa47d6256464e51c1d53394","tid":1029200,"uid":13653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:15:48.000Z","msg":"單拖咁夠薑？"},{"pid":"dbddc93b873184687ff8ab85f214930a3d474914","tid":1029200,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:15:53.000Z","msg":"一定係mk公屋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仔"},{"pid":"77840fb51fef8c66fa5f833d10baea74daa44b50","tid":1029200,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"嘩 岩岩18歲咁就一世 識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"